metadata.name: Roll over again and lie down to win
metadata.description:
Li Shuaixi aimless running, but he didn't know he ran across the road, and even each corner is a 3 without the glasses carefully designed male, even after the duration of each channel are calculated by the dock, seems a mouth has two direction of turning, but had been closed in advance in one direction, he can do is to leave the place as far as possible, stay in, He was afraid zheng Zha would kill him forcibly even if it cost him 1000 points.



Li Shuaixi was an ordinary college student before he came to Main God Space. After four years of comfortable life in college, his body could not withstand any long-term exercise at all. Soon he stopped in a long corridor and panted violently.



Calm down after the fear receded, IQ back to the heights, Li Shuaixi angry one punch hit the wall, "Chu Xuan this bastard, everything is his calculation right! I'll kill him, I'll kill him! '
